| SINGLE BUS BUFFER GATE WITH 3-STATE OUTPUT
| This file contains package information for the following:
|  SOT 5-pin (DBV) package as [Component] LVC1G125_DBV
|  SOT 5-pin (DCK) package as [Component] LVC1G125_DCK
|  NanoStar WCSP 5-pin (YEA) package as [Component] LVC1G125_YEA
|  NanoFree WCSP 5-pin (YZA) package as [Component] LVC1G125_YZA
